terature.architecture-decision-records"}],"anchors":{"tentang-sumber":{"type":"header","text":"Tentang Sumber","value":"tentang-sumber","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"catatan-per-gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Catatan Per Gagasan","value":"catatan-per-gagasan","line":25,"column":0,"depth":2},"1-adr-itu-sebenarnya-apa-dan-kenapa-harus-pendek":{"type":"header","text":"1. ADR itu sebenarnya apa, dan kenapa harus pendek?","value":"1-adr-itu-sebenarnya-apa-dan-kenapa-harus-pendek","line":27,"column":0,"depth":3},"2-kenapa-satu-keputusan-per-dokumen":{"type":"header","text":"2. Kenapa satu keputusan per dokumen?","value":"2-kenapa-satu-keputusan-per-dokumen","line":33,"column":0,"depth":3},"3-kenapa-adr-tidak-boleh-diedit-sembarangan-tapi-harus-di-supersede":{"type":"header","text":"3. Kenapa ADR tidak boleh diedit sembarangan, tapi harus di-supersede?","value":"3-kenapa-adr-tidak-boleh-diedit-sembarangan-tapi-harus-di-supersede","line":39,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-apa-hubungan-adr-dengan-kolaborasi-tim-bukan-cuma-dokumentasi":{"type":"header","text":"4. Apa hubungan ADR dengan kolaborasi tim, bukan cuma dokumentasi?","value":"4-apa-hubungan-adr-dengan-kolaborasi-tim-bukan-cuma-dokumentasi","line":45,"column":0,"depth":3},"5-adr-ini-nyambung-ke-praktik-lain-apa-saja-di-luar-artikel-fowler":{"type":"header","text":"5. ADR ini nyambung ke praktik lain apa saja di luar artikel Fowler?","value":"5-adr-ini-nyambung-ke-praktik-lain-apa-saja-di-luar-artikel-fowler","line":51,"column":0,"depth":3},"zettels-yang-dibuat-dari-sumber-ini":{"type":"header","text":"Zettels yang Dibuat dari Sumber Ini","value":"zettels-yang-dibuat-dari-sumber-ini","line":59,"column":0,"depth":2},"pertanyaan-terbuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan Terbuka","value":"pertanyaan-terbuka","line":67,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ae3bw38eg7l5p3ntry27x87","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"architecture-decision-record--martin-fowler\">Architecture Decision Record — Martin Fowler<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#architecture-decision-record--martin-fowler\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"tentang-sumber\">Tentang Sumber<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tentang-sumber\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Judul</strong>: Architecture Decision Record</li>\n<li><strong>Penulis / Author</strong>: Martin Fowler</li>\n<li><strong>Tahun</strong>: 2011 / revisi artikel Bliki</li>\n<li><strong>Jenis</strong>: artikel web</li>\n<li><strong>Link / ISBN</strong>: <a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/bliki/ArchitectureDecisionRecord.html\">https://martinfowler.com/bliki/ArchitectureDecisionRecord.html</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"catatan-per-gagasan\">Catatan Per Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#catatan-per-gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-adr-itu-sebenarnya-apa-dan-kenapa-harus-pendek\">1. ADR itu sebenarnya apa, dan kenapa harus pendek?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-adr-itu-sebenarnya-apa-dan-kenapa-harus-pendek\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ADR adalah dokumen singkat yang menjelaskan satu keputusan arsitektur, konteksnya, dan konsekuensinya.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue: ADR bukan dokumentasi teknis yang lengkap; ia adalah sistem rekaman alasan. Kalau dokumen terlalu panjang, ia berubah dari alat bantu keputusan jadi beban baca. Itulah alasan Fowler mendorong gaya \"inverted pyramid\": inti keputusan di depan, detail pendukung di belakang.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-kenapa-satu-keputusan-per-dokumen\">2. Kenapa satu keputusan per dokumen?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-kenapa-satu-keputusan-per-dokumen\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Satu ADR per keputusan membantu menjaga batasan yang jelas, timeline yang bersih, dan diskusi tim yang fokus.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue: kalau satu file menggabungkan banyak keputusan, riwayat jadi kabur dan supersede jadi rumit. Satu file = satu unit keputusan yang mudah dipindai dan gampang dilacak.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-kenapa-adr-tidak-boleh-diedit-sembarangan-tapi-harus-di-supersede\">3. Kenapa ADR tidak boleh diedit sembarangan, tapi harus di-supersede?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-kenapa-adr-tidak-boleh-diedit-sembarangan-tapi-harus-di-supersede\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Setelah accepted, ADR harus dibiarkan utuh. Perubahan dibuat lewat ADR baru yang supersede.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue: ini menjaga nilai histori. Keputusan lama mencatat konteks, constraint, dan asumsi saat itu. Mengubah ADR lama sama dengan menghapus jejak pikiran yang pernah memimpin tim.</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-apa-hubungan-adr-dengan-kolaborasi-tim-bukan-cuma-dokumentasi\">4. Apa hubungan ADR dengan kolaborasi tim, bukan cuma dokumentasi?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-apa-hubungan-adr-dengan-kolaborasi-tim-bukan-cuma-dokumentasi\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Fowler menempatkan ADR sebagai medium diskusi dan alignment, bukan sekadar arsip setelah keputusan.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue: proses menulis ADR memaksa tim menimbang alternatif, trade-off, dan masukan. ADR yang sehat adalah scaffold untuk negosiasi keputusan, bukan rasionalisasi setelah fakta.</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-adr-ini-nyambung-ke-praktik-lain-apa-saja-di-luar-artikel-fowler\">5. ADR ini nyambung ke praktik lain apa saja di luar artikel Fowler?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-adr-ini-nyambung-ke-praktik-lain-apa-saja-di-luar-artikel-fowler\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ADR modern terkait dengan praktik seperti MADR, decision log, dan tools ADR.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue: Fowler memberi prinsip ringkas dan riwayat. MADR memberi format Markdown yang konsisten. Sementara praktik decision log menekankan bahwa riwayat keputusan bernilai untuk tim baru, audit, dan adaptasi.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"zettels-yang-dibuat-dari-sumber-ini\">Zettels yang Dibuat dari Sumber Ini<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#zettels-yang-dibuat-dari-sumber-ini\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055413\">ADR adalah decision log yang merekam alasan, bukan dokumentasi desain</a> — ADR adalah decision log yang merekam alasan, bukan dokumentasi desain</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055414\">Satu keputusan per ADR menjaga batasan dan riwayat yang bersih</a> — Satu keputusan per ADR menjaga batasan dan riwayat yang bersih</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055415\">ADR accepted harus disupersede, bukan diedit ulang</a> — ADR accepted harus disupersede, bukan diedit ulang</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055619\">ADR sehat memaksa maintainer mengubah perilaku, bukan sekadar menambah dokumen</a> — ADR sehat memaksa maintainer mengubah perilaku, bukan sekadar menambah dokumen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055738\">Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram</a> — Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-terbuka\">Pertanyaan Terbuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-terbuka\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Kapan keputusan arsitektur layak di-ADR-kan, dan kapan cukup diarahkan lewat dokumentasi lain?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana tim menjaga ADR tetap ringan tanpa kehilangan nilai historis?</li>\n<li>Apa batas praktis antara \"keputusan arsitektur signifikan\" dan \"keputusan implementasi biasa\"?</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #154406;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.literature-note\">literature-note</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">adr (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">decision-making (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055413\">ADR adalah decision log yang merekam alasan, bukan dokumentasi desain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055414\">Satu keputusan per ADR menjaga batasan dan riwayat yang bersih</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055415\">ADR accepted harus disupersede, bukan diedit ulang</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055619\">ADR sehat memaksa maintainer mengubah perilaku, bukan sekadar menambah dokumen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055738\">Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"